Sam?

44
00:06:59.414 --> 00:07:00.848
Sam Nelson?

45
00:07:01.382 --> 00:07:02.377
Yeah.

46
00:07:02.889 --> 00:07:04.618
Mei Tan.

47
00:07:04.754 --> 00:07:07.484
Uh. there's no way
you'd remember me.

48
00:07:07.619 --> 00:07:09.361
Singapore.

49
